4.11	Kay_Harker	Kay Harker	Kay Harker is a fictional character, the young hero of the books The Midnight Folk and The Box of Delights by John Masefield, and the BBC series based on The Box of Delights. The series ran in 1984, where the character was played by actor Devin Stanfield. Kay is of an unspecified age, and the book follows his adventures one Christmas Holiday alongside his contemporaries who are staying for the holidays.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/0a/Box_Of_Delights_DVD_Cover.jpg/220px-Box_Of_Delights_DVD_Cover.jpg
